<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>一名三岁女童</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">在跟随外婆来小区</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">探望曾祖母的过程中</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>不慎从8楼楼梯间窗户坠落</span></strong></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
